nodes.text: A Gungan militiagung was a soldier in the army of the warlord Boss Rogoe during the war between the Gungan tribes in the year 3000 BBY. The militiagung was ordered to lead a tribes of bursas to destroy Otoh Sancture, and after the attack encountered the cities leader, Gallo, who discovered Rogoe had been responsible for Otoh Sancture's destruction.
The militiagung's voice is heard in Star Wars: Galactic Battlegrounds, but the game does not specify which Gungan it is supposed to be.
